=head3 SVG and MathML

=over

=item C<< SVG(... PairList attrs, Array children ) → HTMLElement >>

Represents an SVG container and coordinate system, including SVG embedded in HTML.

=cut

function SVG(... PairList attrs, Array children ) → HTMLElement {
	return html_tag( "svg", ...attrs, ...children );
}

=item C<< MATH(... PairList attrs, Array children ) → HTMLElement >>

Represents the top-level MathML element for mathematical markup.

